‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Layout.idr         # Struct layout proofs (952 bytes, 8-byte aligned)
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Foreign.idr        # FFI declarations with safety proofs
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ocaml/                 # Offline Scheme transformer (not HPC)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ada/                   # Terminal UI (standalone)
